Uses hpl-2.2 sources: https://www.netlib.org/benchmark/hpl/hpl-2.2.tar.gz


Unpack tarball into /srv/pihome

ln -s /srv/pihome/hpl-2.2 /home/mythicuser/hpl-2.2

sudo apt -y install libatlas-base-dev libmpich-dev libmpich2-3 gfortran libopenblas-dev 

Build with 'Make.rpi' makefile:
cp /home/pi/terrible_pi/hpl/Make.rpi .
cd setup
make generic
cd ..
make arch=rpi
cd bin/rpi
cp /home/pi/terrible_pi/hpl/run_hpl .
cp /home/pi/terrible_pi/hpl/nodes .
cp /home/pi/terrible_pi/hpl/HPL.dat .
cd

Copy HPL.dat, run_hpl, and nodes to /srv/pihome/hpl-2.2/bin/rpi

Boot all nodes, then:
	pdsh -R ssh -w node[1-4] "sudo apt install mpich"

